description: Data recored from an access control list change message and its associated access control list object and the acl's dbo.

changeNumber.description: The application change number created as a result of this change.

aclId.description: The ID of the access control list object.

etag.description: The etag of the change message.

timestamp.description: The timestamp of the change event, in UTC milliseconds.

changeType.description: The type of a change event.

objectId.description: The ID of the owner object. (From the DboAccessControlList)

objectType.description: The type of the owner object. (From the DboAccessControlList)
